al Gear Survive]]'' || Player, MB Soldiers || \n|<ref name=\"btva\" />\n|-\n|''Epic Seven'' || Charles ||\n|-\n|''Marvel Powers United VR'' || [[Loki (comics)|Loki]] || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Lego DC Super-Villains]]'' || Firefly, [[Roy Harper (comics)|Arsenal]], Riddler Goon || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | {{dts|2019|01|29|format=y}} || ''[[Kingdom Hearts III]]'' || Will Turner || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Metro Exodus]]'' || Admiral, Soldier || || &nbsp;\n|-\n|''[[Days Gone]]'' || Mark \"Cope\" Copeland || || &nbsp;\n|-\n|''[[Judgment (video game)|Judgment]]'' || Masaharu Kaito || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Marvel Ultimate Alliance 3: The Black Order]]'' || [[Gorgon (Inhuman)|Gorgon]] || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n|''[[The Outer Worlds]]'' || Charles Rockwell || || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt9417446/fullcredits|title=The Outer Worlds (2019 Video Game)|publisher=|via=www.imdb.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n<!-- NEED SOURCE\n{{Div col||30em}}\n* ''[[The Amazing Spider-Man (2012 video game)|The Amazing Spider-Man]]'' \u2013 Additional voices\n* ''[[Atelier Iris: Eternal Mana]]'' \u2013 Delsus (uncredited)\n* ''[[Batman: Arkham City]]'' \u2013 Political Prisoners, Officer Michaels, Ernest Ray\n* ''[[Beat Down: Fists of Vengeance]]'' \u2013 Eugene (uncredited)\n* ''[[Bioshock 2]]'' \u2013 Additional voices\n* ''[[Breakdown (video game)|Breakdown]]'' \u2013 Solus (uncredited)\n* ''[[Call of Duty: Black Ops II]]'' \u2013 Additional voices\n* ''[[Castlevania: Portrait of Ruin]]'' \u2013 English ADR Director\n* ''[[Champions: Return to Arms]]'' \u2013 Vai Shir Cat Warrior\n* ''[[Company of Heroes]]'' \u2013 Airborne Commander\n* ''[[Death by Degrees]]'' \u2013 Alan Smithee (uncredited)\n* ''[[Destiny (video game)|Destiny]]'' \u2013 Guardian: Awoken Male<ref>{{cite video| title = Destiny - End Credits - IGN Video| url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2014/09/11/destiny-end-credits| work=IGN Video| date=2014-09-11| accessdate=2014-12-04| at=4:30