 of Warcraft: Warlords of Draenor]]''<ref>{{Cite video game | title = World of Warcraft: Warlords of Draenor | year = 2014 | scene=Closing credits, 11:30 in, Voice Over Cast | developer=[[Blizzard Entertainment]] }}</ref> \u2013 Vindicator Maraad\n* ''[[Zatch Bell! Mamodo Battles]]'' \u2013 Albert, Gustav, Wonrei\n{{div col end}}\n--->\n\n===Other dubbing===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of voice performances in other dubbing\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Source<ref name=\"resume\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Oldboy (2003 film)|Oldboy]]'' || Lee Woo-jin || || <ref name=\"ca\"/>\n|}<!-- NEED SOURCE\n* ''[[Steven Spielberg|The Porpeen]]'' \u2013 Xevious (Voice only)\n* ''[[Versus (film)|Versus]]'' \u2013 Ponytail, One-handed Sidekick (English dub, credited as Mark Percy)\n* ''[[XX: Beautiful Beast]]'' \u2013 Yoichi Fujinami (English dub, credited as Mark Percy)\n--->\n\n===Live-action===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of appearances in film and television\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Source<ref name=\"resume\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2008|07|03|format=y}} || ''[[Adventures in Voice Acting]]'' || Himself || || <ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.adventuresinvoiceacting.com/wp-content/uploads/press_kit/aiva_v1_press_release_12-04-07_AiVA_NY_Anime_Fest.pdf | title=Bang Zoom! Entertainment to Preview Adventures in Voice Acting Documentary at New York Anime Festival | work=Adventures in Voice Acting | date=December 4, 2007 | access-date=September 17, 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074601/http://www.adventuresinvoiceacting.com/wp-content/uploads/press_kit/aiva_v1_press_release_12-04-07_AiVA_NY_Anime_Fest.pdf | archive-date=October 6, 2014 | url-status=dead | df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|}<!-- NEED SOURCE\n* ''Anime: Drawing a Revolution'' \u2013 Himself\n* ''[[Important Things with Demetri Martin]]'' \u